race.comment: CANYA MAYHEM (8) was a last start winner (29.43) from Box 4 at this track. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Can continue on his winning ways. MEPUNGA SHINE (2) has a strong record this track and trip with six wins and two placings from 11 starts. Missed the frame latest (30.82) when fifth over 530m at Angle Park in a OPEN. Looks suited here and can measure up. VINCENT BALE (4) boasts a strong record this journey here with eight wins and six minors from 23 tries. Below best last time at Wentworth Park (30.24) in a NG, finishing a 6 length sixth. Looks one of the chances. PAW ULTRA (1) cannot be left out after placing last start.
